headline.main: TURKS SHOW MIGHT TO AXIS OBSERVERS; Modern Equipment Paraded, Planes Flown Over Cities on Republic's Birthday

lead_paragraph: ANKARA, Turkey, Oct. 29 -- The Turkish Republic celebrated its eighteenth anniversary today with in impressive display of military might in huge parades and marches-past in the Turkish capital and in Istanbul.
abstract: Pres Inonu reaffirms Turkish readiness to guard neutrality
